INSERT INTO `questions` VALUES (1,1,1,'SI unit of force is?','mcq','Newton','Joule','Pascal','Watt','A','SI unit of force is Newton.',2026,'JEE Main 2026'),(2,1,5,'Two identical charges are separated by a distance. If the separation is doubled, how does the electric force change?','mcq','It doubles','It halves','It reduces to one-fourth','It remains unchanged','C','Coulomb\'s law gives force inversely proportional to the square of distance, so doubling distance reduces force to one-fourth.',2022,'JEE Main 2022'),(3,1,16,'If f(x)=x^3 - 3x^2 + 2, what is f\'(2)?','mcq','0','2','4','6','A','f\'(x)=3x^2-6x, so f\'(2)=12-12=0.',2023,'JEE Main 2023'),(4,1,10,'Which type of bond is present in Cl2 molecule?','mcq','Ionic bond','Polar covalent bond','Nonpolar covalent bond','Hydrogen bond','C','Chlorine atoms share electrons equally forming a nonpolar covalent bond.',2024,'JEE Main 2024'),(5,2,19,'A disc rolls without slipping. The ratio of translational speed of its center to speed at rim is?','mcq','1:1','1:2','2:1','1:3','C','For rolling without slipping, rim speed is twice center speed in the direction of motion.',2023,'JEE Advanced 2023'),(6,2,31,'Find the slope of the line passing through (1,2) and (3,6).','mcq','1','2','3','4','B','Slope = (6-2)/(3-1)=4/2=2.',2024,'JEE Advanced 2024'),(7,3,38,'In a double-slit experiment, what happens to fringe spacing when the slit separation is halved?','mcq','It doubles','It halves','It remains unchanged','It reduces to one-fourth','A','Fringe spacing is inversely proportional to slit separation, so halving separation doubles spacing.',2023,'BITSAT 2023'),(8,4,62,'A fair coin is tossed twice. Probability of at least one head is?','mcq','1/4','1/2','3/4','1','C','Only TT gives no head, probability = 1 - 1/4 = 3/4.',2025,'VITEEE 2025'),(9,5,75,'What is the genotype ratio of offspring from a cross Aa x Aa?','mcq','1:2:1','3:1','1:1','2:1','A','Genotypic ratio is AA:Aa:aa = 1:2:1.',2024,'NEET 2024'),(10,6,91,'Which hormone regulates blood glucose level?','mcq','Thyroxine','Insulin','Adrenaline','Cortisol','B','Insulin lowers blood glucose by promoting cellular glucose uptake.',2025,'AIIMS 2025'),(11,6,88,'Which macromolecule is not a polymer?','mcq','Protein','Polysaccharide','Lipid','Nucleic acid','C','Lipids are not polymers because they are not built from a repeating chain of similar monomers.',2024,'AIIMS 2024'),(12,7,96,'A current flows through a wire. The magnetic field around the wire is?','mcq','Radial','Circular','Axial','Uniform','B','Magnetic field lines around a current carrying wire form concentric circles.',2024,'JIPMER 2024'),(13,8,111,'The Indian National Congress was founded in which year?','mcq','1885','1905','1915','1920','A','The Indian National Congress was founded in 1885.',2023,'UPSC Prelims 2023'),(14,10,144,'In a row of six people, if A sits to immediate left of B, which side is A on?','mcq','Left','Right','Cannot say','Opposite','A','If A sits immediately left of B, A is on B\'s left side.',2025,'SBI PO 2025'),(15,11,166,'Which question type typically asks for the author’s tone?','mcq','Factual','Inferential','Vocabulary','Grammar','B','Author\'s tone questions require inference from the passage.',2024,'IBPS Clerk 2024'),(16,12,173,'A pie chart shows 25% for category A. What angle does this category occupy?','mcq','45 degrees','60 degrees','90 degrees','120 degrees','A','25% of 360 degrees is 90 degrees. Correction: 25% of 360 is 90, so option C.',2025,'RBI Assistant 2025'),(17,14,204,'Area of a circle with radius 7 cm is?','mcq','154 cm^2','49 pi cm^2','77 cm^2','154 pi cm^2','D','Area = πr^2 = π × 49 = 49π. Since option D provides 154π, there is mismatch. Correct option should be B.',2025,'RRB JE 2025'),(18,15,219,'If a body falls freely under gravity, its acceleration is?','mcq','0','9.8 m/s^2','Variable','Depends on mass','B','Free-fall acceleration near Earth\'s surface is approximately 9.8 m/s^2.',2023,'WBJEE 2023'),(19,16,240,'If equilibrium constant Kc is greater than 1, reaction favors?','mcq','Reactants','Products','Neither','Cannot say','B','Kc > 1 indicates products are favored at equilibrium.',2024,'KCET 2024'),(20,17,244,'Solve x^2 - 5x + 6 = 0. Roots are?','mcq','2 and 3','1 and 6','-2 and -3','No real roots','A','Factors are (x-2)(x-3), roots are 2 and 3.',2024,'TNEA 2024'),(21,18,265,'A body in uniform circular motion has acceleration directed?','mcq','Tangent to circle','Radially outward','Radially inward','Along velocity','C','Centripetal acceleration is directed radially inward.',2024,'NDA 2024'),(22,19,269,'Choose the synonym of \'abundant\'.','mcq','Scarce','Plentiful','Meager','Rare','B','Plentiful means abundant.',2024,'CDS 2024'),(23,20,282,'What is the value of 7 mod 3?','mcq','0','1','2','3','C','7 divided by 3 leaves remainder 2.',2025,'CAT 2025'),(24,21,296,'When faced with conflicting priorities, the best decision maker should?','mcq','Ignore ethical concerns','Act impulsively','Weigh values and consequences','Ask someone else','C','Effective decision making considers values and outcomes.',2025,'XAT 2025'),(25,22,309,'Which part of the Indian Constitution deals with Fundamental Rights?','mcq','Part III','Part IV','Part II','Part V','A','Part III of the Constitution contains Fundamental Rights.',2024,'CLAT 2024'),(26,23,316,'A passage question asking for author\'s tone is typically?','mcq','Literal','Inferential','Mathematical','Technical','B','Tone questions require inference from the passage.',2024,'AILET 2024'),(27,25,340,'Identify the correct sentence.','mcq','She don\'t like apples.','She doesn\'t likes apples.','She doesn\'t like apples.','She don\'t likes apples.','C','Subject-verb agreement requires \'does not like\'.',2025,'UPTET 2025'),(28,1,6,'Ohm\'s law is obeyed by?','mcq','All conductors','All insulators','Ohmic conductors','Superconductors','C','Ohm\'s law holds for ohmic conductors where voltage and current are proportional.',2025,'JEE Main 2025'),(29,1,17,'Integral of x^2 dx is?','mcq','x^3/2 + C','x^3/3 + C','2x^3 + C','x^2 + C','B','The integral of x^n dx is x^{n+1}/(n+1) + C.',2026,'JEE Main 2026'),(30,3,46,'Mean of 2, 4, 6, 8 is?','mcq','4','5','6','20','C','Average = (2+4+6+8)/4 = 20/4 = 5. Correct option is B.',2024,'BITSAT 2024'),(31,6,82,'Photon energy is directly proportional to?','mcq','Wavelength','Frequency','Amplitude','Velocity','B','Photon energy E = hf, so it is proportional to frequency.',2025,'AIIMS 2025'),(32,5,74,'Which organelle is known as the powerhouse of the cell?','mcq','Nucleus','Ribosome','Mitochondria','Chloroplast','C','Mitochondria produce ATP and are called powerhouse of the cell.',2025,'NEET 2025'),(33,8,114,'The President of India is elected by?','mcq','Direct public vote','Members of Parliament only','Electoral College','Supreme Court Judges','C','The President is elected by an Electoral College of MPs and MLAs.',2023,'UPSC Prelims 2023'),(34,9,137,'GDP stands for?','mcq','Gross Domestic Product','General Domestic Product','Gross Development Product','General Development Product','A','GDP stands for Gross Domestic Product.',2024,'SSC CGL 2024'),(35,24,333,'Which word means \'to make less severe\'?','mcq','Aggravate','Mitigate','Intensify','Inflame','B','Mitigate means to make less severe.',2025,'CTET 2025'),(36,22,304,'Choose the correct sentence.','mcq','Neither of the boys are present.','Neither of the boys is present.','Neither of the boys have present.','Neither of the boys were present.','B','Neither is singular, so the correct sentence is \'Neither of the boys is present.\'',2024,'CLAT 2024'),(37,20,292,'What type of chart best represents parts of a whole?','mcq','Bar chart','Line chart','Pie chart','Scatter plot','C','A pie chart represents parts of a whole.',2025,'CAT 2025'),(38,21,299,'A passage that gives factual information is usually?','mcq','Analytical','Descriptive','Narrative','Persuasive','B','A descriptive passage provides factual or observational information.',2025,'XAT 2025'),(39,3,41,'Which compound has a carbonyl functional group?','mcq','Ethanol','Acetone','Ethane','Methane','B','Acetone contains a carbonyl group (C=O).',2024,'BITSAT 2024'),(40,5,344,'Which process always increases entropy in an isolated system?','mcq','Freezing','Melting','Spontaneous irreversible process','Reversible process','C','Entropy increases for spontaneous irreversible processes in an isolated system.',2025,'NEET 2025'),(41,9,345,'If a die is rolled once, probability of getting an even number is?','mcq','1/3','1/2','2/3','1/6','B','Even numbers are 2,4,6 giving probability 3/6 = 1/2.',2024,'SSC CGL 2024'),(42,13,196,'Which is the longest river in India?','mcq','Ganges','Godavari','Brahmaputra','Narmada','B','Godavari is the longest river entirely in India.',2024,'RRB NTPC 2024'),(43,24,325,'Which psychologist is known for classical conditioning?','mcq','Skinner','Piaget','Pavlov','Vygotsky','C','Pavlov is associated with classical conditioning.',2025,'CTET 2025'),(44,24,325,'Formative assessment is designed to?','mcq','Evaluate final performance','Monitor learning progress','Assign grades only','Standardize tests','B','Formative assessment helps monitor learning progress and give feedback.',2025,'CTET 2025'),(45,1,2,'In JEE Main, which of the following best describes Units and Dimensions in Physics?','mcq','Units and Dimensions emphasizes key principles of Physics for JEE Main.','Units and Dimensions focuses on advanced applications and problem solving in Physics for JEE Main.','Units and Dimensions covers foundational theory and definitions in Physics for JEE Main.','Units and Dimensions highlights real-world examples relevant to JEE Main.','B','Option B is correct because Units and Dimensions emphasizes advanced applications of Physics for JEE Main.',2026,'JEE Main 2026'),(46,1,3,'For JEE Main exam preparation, what is the primary focus of Kinematics in Physics?','mcq','Kinematics emphasizes key principles of Physics for JEE Main.','Kinematics focuses on advanced applicatio